com.blazegraph.gremlin.structure

Class BlazeGraph.GraphStreamer<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.blazegraph.gremlin.structure.BlazeGraph.GraphStreamer<E>
  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of Sesame element (BindingSet or Statement)
    Enclosing class:
    BlazeGraph

    protected class BlazeGraph.GraphStreamer<E>
extends Object
    Convert a Sesame iteration into a Java 8 Stream. Backed by database resources so these streams must be closed when finished. (Does not close the connection but will close the Sesame iteration / Blaze iterators).
    Author:
    mikepersonick

    • Constructor Detail

      • GraphStreamer

        public GraphStreamer(info.aduna.iteration.CloseableIteration<E,?> result,
                     Optional<Runnable> onClose)
        Construct a streamer using the supplied Sesame iteration and optional onClose() behavior. The iteration will be closed automatically by this class, so the onClose code does not need to do it.
